  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the monkfish and cook until browned on all sides",
    "Add the Arborio rice and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Add the chopped nuka-pickle and stir to combine",
    "Add the heavy cream and bring to a simmer",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 20 minutes",
    "Serve hot and enjoy"
